        Constructs a new QVT Transformation to Alloy translator. A QVTRelation2Alloy is called for every top QVT Relation and direction.
        Parameters:
        qvt - the QVT Transformation being translated
        statesigs - maps transformation arguments (or metamodels) to the respective Alloy singleton signature (or abstract signature)
        modelsigs - maps metamodels to the set of Alloy signatures
